    "But if I wanted something really fast, then I would do the complete solution (baseline help). \"",
    "Similarly, P15 stated her preference would vary by situation, explaining, \"I think if I just want a quick way to solve that question, I'll go to the regular one (baseline). \"",
    "In this section, we discuss how CodeTailor addressed the rising concerns when applying generative AI in educational contexts, future steps to tackle challenges in CodeTailor, and implications for broader AI-based support design.",
    "Address the concerns of LLMs in educationTwo growing concerns about using GenAI in education are (1) students using AI to generate answers and finish the activity without learning (over-reliance), and (2) AI mistakes that can mislead novices [30,35].",
    "Motivated by these concerns, CodeTailor harnesses LLMs to generate correct, engaging, and personalized scaffolding to support development of basic programming skills at scale.CodeTailor tries to address the concern of over-reliance through several aspects."
